162
00:08:58,647 --> 00:09:01,559
Barty. Good to see you.

163
00:09:01,607 --> 00:09:02,835
Sit down there.

164
00:09:02,887 --> 00:09:05,037
(Laughing)

165
00:09:05,087 --> 00:09:07,661
