Anything.

200
00:11:16,887 --> 00:11:19,807
I have had trouble
getting the English papers.

201
00:11:19,847 --> 00:11:23,476
–Would it be possible…
–Except the English papers.

202
00:11:23,527 --> 00:11:26,847
Anything else, just ask.
Except the English papers.

203
00:11:26,887 --> 00:11:30,167
