210
00:11:50,127 --> 00:11:52,727
No, not leprosy.
But there's something wrong.

211
00:11:52,767 --> 00:11:54,807
Did you never think
how strange it was,

212
00:11:54,847 --> 00:11:57,407
three priests living alone
on an island?

213
00:11:57,447 --> 00:11:59,165
I suppose…

214
00:11:59,207 --> 00:12:02,647
