352
00:19:23,847 --> 00:19:25,695
Don't start celebrating yet.

353
00:19:25,727 --> 00:19:28,087
Remember we've got
one more act to go.

354
00:19:28,127 --> 00:19:30,766
Ladies and gentlemen,
please welcome…

355
